%N A015450 Inverse of 1441st cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015450 Periodic with period length 1441. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015450 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015450/b015450.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015450 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1441.
%H A015450 <a href="/index/Rec#order_1300">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 1300.
%H A015450 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015450 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015450 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1441,x],{x,0,140}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, May 20 2017 *)
%o A015450 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1441)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
%K A015450 sign,easy,changed
%O A015450 0,1
%A A015450 _Simon Plouffe_
